				<p>Choose the &lt;a href=&quot;<a href="http://www.hospitalkhoj.com/mental.htm&#038;quot" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'outbound-comment', 'http://www.hospitalkhoj.com/mental.htm&amp;quot', 'http://www.hospitalkhoj.com/mental.htm&amp;quot']);"  rel="nofollow">http://www.hospitalkhoj.com/mental.htm&#038;quot</a>; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt; top mental hospitals in India&lt;/a&gt; according to your disorder, for instance, some hospitals are known to provide best heart treatments while some are recognized for their standard orthopedic treatments, etc. Thus, it is always better to decide the hospital as per the kind of ailment you are suffering from. &lt;br /&gt;</p>
			</div>
